  "url": "https://blog.realpics.cn/archives/468",
  "title": "对几块SSD的测试 – STLIN的博客",
  "html": "<main class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-vertical is-content-justification-stretch is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-6215b345 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-post-title has-x-large-font-size\">对几块SSD的测试</h1>\n<div class=\"wp-block-template-part\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-content-justification-left is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-dfe8e91f wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-post-date\"><time datetime=\"2025-10-15T09:00:17+08:00\"><a href=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/archives/468\">10 月 15, 2025</a></time></div>\n<p class=\"has-contrast-2-color has-text-color\">—</p>\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size has-contrast-2-color has-text-color\">由</p>\n<div class=\"wp-block-post-author-name\"><a class=\"wp-block-post-author-name__link\" href=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/archives/author/shantoulin\" target=\"_self\">shantoulin</a></div>\n<div class=\"taxonomy-category wp-block-post-terms\"><span class=\"wp-block-post-terms__prefix\">于 </span><a href=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/archives/category/%e6%8a%98%e8%85%be\" rel=\"tag\">折腾</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"entry-content alignfull wp-block-post-content has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-post-content-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p>下面是测试机配置</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><tbody><tr><td>CPU</td><td>Ryzen 7 5700X@PBO+200</td></tr><tr><td>RAM</td><td>32G DDR4 3000 C18</td></tr><tr><td>MotherBoard</td><td>ASUS TUF B450M PRO S V4601</td></tr><tr><td>System</td><td>Ubuntu 24.04</td></tr><tr><td>SSD1</td><td>WD SN560 1T run on pcie 3.0</td></tr><tr><td>SSD2</td><td>Samsung 860Evo 1T 64TBW</td></tr><tr><td>SSD3</td><td>Samsung 860Evo 1T 96TBW</td></tr><tr><td>SSD4</td><td>Kingston SA400 120G</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<p>我们使用<strong>KDiskMark</strong>进行测试，测试大小为1G5轮</p>\n<p>WD SN560 1T run on pcie 3.0</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-469\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"506\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" src=\"readmes/images/rss_5abc3fc386.png\" width=\"599\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-470\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"506\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" src=\"readmes/images/rss_9df9e2733c.png\" width=\"599\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-471\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"506\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" src=\"readmes/images/rss_c5060a3866.png\" width=\"599\"/></figure>\n<p>Samsung 860Evo 1T 64TBW</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-472\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"506\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" src=\"readmes/images/rss_3b565ad85d.png\" width=\"599\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-473\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"506\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" src=\"readmes/images/rss_1d1706d8d9.png\" width=\"599\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-484\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"506\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" src=\"readmes/images/rss_2202c5ff74.png\" width=\"599\"/></figure>\n<p>Samsung 860Evo 1T 96TBW</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-475\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"506\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" src=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/42e66085f080fd827872ea72f888cf4f.png\" srcset=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/42e66085f080fd827872ea72f888cf4f.png 599w, https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/42e66085f080fd827872ea72f888cf4f-300x253.png 300w\" width=\"599\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-476\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"506\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" src=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/2a556be7b926e50ae2b7b26eca9d3f54.png\" srcset=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/2a556be7b926e50ae2b7b26eca9d3f54.png 599w, https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/2a556be7b926e50ae2b7b26eca9d3f54-300x253.png 300w\" width=\"599\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-477\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"506\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" src=\"readmes/images/rss_d70e3745e3.png\" width=\"599\"/></figure>\n<p>Kingston SA400 120G</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-478\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"506\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" src=\"readmes/images/rss_cdde5d9066.png\" width=\"599\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-479\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"506\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" src=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/7093febabe499177d2c14b39993bf308.png\" srcset=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/7093febabe499177d2c14b39993bf308.png 599w, https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/7093febabe499177d2c14b39993bf308-300x253.png 300w\" width=\"599\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-481\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"506\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" src=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/579f5c47ef6ec1a6631676a8b711c74a.png\" srcset=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/579f5c47ef6ec1a6631676a8b711c74a.png 599w, https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/579f5c47ef6ec1a6631676a8b711c74a-300x253.png 300w\" width=\"599\"/></figure>\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">各SSD性能测试数据汇总 (单位: MB/s)</h3>\n<p>下表汇总了所有SSD在KDiskMark中的性能表现（速度单位为MB/s）。</p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>最优值</strong>使用 <strong>🏆</strong> 标记。</li>\n<li><strong>最差值</strong>使用 <strong>🔻</strong> 标记。</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><tbody><tr><td>测试项目 (单位: MB/s)</td><td>WD SN560 1T (NVMe)</td><td>Samsung 860 Evo 1T (64TBW)</td><td>Samsung 860 Evo 1T (96TBW)</td><td>Kingston SA400 120G</td></tr><tr><td><strong>SEQ1M Q8T1 读取</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 3485.22</strong></td><td>554.74</td><td>554.45</td><td><strong>🔻 514.54</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>SEQ1M Q8T1 写入</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 2748.89</strong></td><td>527.08</td><td>526.55</td><td><strong>🔻 375.06</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>SEQ1M Q1T1 读取</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 2646.40</strong></td><td>519.61</td><td>520.54</td><td><strong>🔻 457.94</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>SEQ1M Q1T1 写入</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 2016.44</strong></td><td>476.81</td><td>475.86</td><td><strong>🔻 358.91</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>RND4K Q32T1 读取</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 916.43</strong></td><td>397.70</td><td>395.36</td><td><strong>🔻 163.55</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>RND4K Q32T1 写入</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 689.56</strong></td><td>371.26</td><td>370.23</td><td><strong>🔻 327.86</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>RND4K Q1T1 读取</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 70.89</strong></td><td>45.42</td><td>49.77</td><td><strong>🔻 27.88</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>RND4K Q1T1 写入</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 214.31</strong></td><td>130.78</td><td>131.74</td><td><strong>🔻 96.95</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-487\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"804\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"readmes/images/rss_408dd7db16.png\" width=\"1024\"/></figure>\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">各SSD性能测试数据汇总 (IOPS)</h3>\n<p>IOPS (Input/Output Operations Per Second) 反映磁盘处理零碎文件的能力，越高越好。</p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>最优值 (越高越好)</strong> 使用 <strong>🏆</strong> 标记。</li>\n<li><strong>最差值 (越低越好)</strong> 使用 <strong>🔻</strong> 标记。</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><tbody><tr><td>测试项目 (单位: IOPS)</td><td>WD SN560 1T (NVMe)</td><td>Samsung 860 Evo 1T (64TBW)</td><td>Samsung 860 Evo 1T (96TBW)</td><td>Kingston SA400 120G</td></tr><tr><td><strong>RND4K Q32T1 读取</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 229,107.67</strong></td><td>99,425.20</td><td>98,840.70</td><td><strong>🔻 40,888.01</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>RND4K Q32T1 写入</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 172,389.56</strong></td><td>92,815.02</td><td>92,558.55</td><td><strong>🔻 81,964.33</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>RND4K Q1T1 读取</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 17,723.18</strong></td><td>11,354.25</td><td>12,442.31</td><td><strong>🔻 6,970.05</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>RND4K Q1T1 写入</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 53,578.56</strong></td><td>32,695.93</td><td>32,933.90</td><td><strong>🔻 24,238.10</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-488\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"802\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"readmes/images/rss_ef7bb3c666.png\" width=\"1024\"/></figure>\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">各SSD性能测试数据汇总 (延迟 – Latency) </h3>\n<p>延迟 (Latency) 指的是完成一次请求的平均时间，单位微秒(µs)，<strong>数值越低越好</strong>。</p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>最优值 (越低越好)</strong> 使用 <strong>🏆</strong> 标记。</li>\n<li><strong>最差值 (越高越好)</strong> 使用 <strong>🔻</strong> 标记。</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><tbody><tr><td>测试项目 (单位: µs)</td><td>WD SN560 1T (NVMe)</td><td>Samsung 860 Evo 1T (64TBW)</td><td>Samsung 860 Evo 1T (96TBW)</td><td>Kingston SA400 120G</td></tr><tr><td><strong>SEQ1M Q8T1 读取</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 2,341.72</strong></td><td>14,735.84</td><td>14,745.68</td><td><strong>🔻 15,891.31</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>SEQ1M Q8T1 写入</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 2,888.63</strong></td><td>15,411.22</td><td>15,413.39</td><td><strong>🔻 21,699.99</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>SEQ1M Q1T1 读取</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 388.56</strong></td><td>1,969.42</td><td>1,965.98</td><td><strong>🔻 2,235.30</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>SEQ1M Q1T1 写入</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 423.40</strong></td><td>2,049.34</td><td>2,054.57</td><td><strong>🔻 2,762.60</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>RND4K Q32T1 读取</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 139.37</strong></td><td>321.54</td><td>323.45</td><td><strong>🔻 782.37</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>RND4K Q32T1 写入</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 184.98</strong></td><td>343.68</td><td>344.84</td><td><strong>🔻 391.29</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>RND4K Q1T1 读取</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 56.11</strong></td><td>87.69</td><td>80.01</td><td><strong>🔻 143.02</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>RND4K Q1T1 写入</strong></td><td><strong>🏆 17.78</strong></td><td>29.71</td><td>29.60</td><td><strong>🔻 40.53</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-489\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"807\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"readmes/images/rss_4930484857.png\" width=\"1024\"/></figure>\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-491\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"768\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"readmes/images/rss_d6ed2899df.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-494\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"768\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/3d3792a82a8e61f658264b4b0d88bd5d-1024x768.jpg\" srcset=\"https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/3d3792a82a8e61f658264b4b0d88bd5d-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/3d3792a82a8e61f658264b4b0d88bd5d-300x225.jpg 300w, https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/3d3792a82a8e61f658264b4b0d88bd5d-768x576.jpg 768w, https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/3d3792a82a8e61f658264b4b0d88bd5d-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://blog.realpics.cn/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/3d3792a82a8e61f658264b4b0d88bd5d-2048x1536.jpg 2048w\" width=\"1024\"/></figure>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\">\n</div>\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-contrast-3-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-contrast-3-background-color has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\"/>\n<div class=\"wp-block-comments wp-block-comments-query-loop\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">评论</h2>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-comments-title\" id=\"comments\">《“对几块SSD的测试”》 有 1 条评论</h3>\n<ol class=\"wp-